Version 2.1.6: (2015-08-01):
	* src/Makefile.am (libguile_dbi_la_LIBADD): Remove '-lz'.
	* src/test/Makefile.am (libguile_dbd_test_la_LIBADD): Remove '-lz'.
	* configure.ac: New option '--with-guile-site-dir' to set 'guilesitedir'.
	* Clear prior dlsym errors before they propagate into guile-dbi.
	* Fix random crashes due to bad interaction with garbage collector.

Version 2.1.5: (2013-04-11):
	* Cleaned up README, TODO files.
	* Missing use of guile-config in test directory.
	* Fix .so vs. .dylib dynalically loadable lib issue for Mac OSX.
	* Remove deprecated guile function warnings.

Version 2.1.4: (2010-05-21):
	* Use guile-config to get library, include-file locations.
	* Add a pkg-config guile-dbi.pc file.

Version 2.1.3: (2010-05-18):
	* Remove deprecated header file guile/gh.h from test case.
	* Addition of sqlite3-dbd from Julian Kalbhenn <jkal@gmx.net> and tantalum@online.de
	* Updated documentation, example usage.

Version 2.1.2 (2008-11-24):
	* Patch from Mike Gran, fixes function names in assert.
	* Minor cleanup; avoid un-needed malloc/free.

2008-09-15 Linas Vepstas <linasvepstas@gmail.com>

	* Numerous bug fixes for crashes, hangs, memory leaks.
	* Bump version to release 2.1.1

